Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,玛索 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呵…呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,恶化地这么快的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗 你们要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多大家都到极限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 大叔 会被盯上的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,玛索 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,库奇巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人生的伟大死的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我们岛上群众的幸福生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她牺牲自己 一生毫不利己专门利人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们懂得她生命的价值吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能被你们这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能被你们这种人夺去她的性命！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你在搞什么飞机 你这混蛋白痴豆芽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋白痴豆芽菜…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,别 别来碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你想白白寻死吗 大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别废话！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这才不是废话！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.93,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1106,995)}thymia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你又不能发动情念力！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真难看…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真难看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,留有感情的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,总是活在憎恨与愤怒之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是难看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,难看或许是我们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.51,0:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可没道理被你们这些蒙面杀人狂说！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,下不了手么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去报台霞姐姐的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,够了…不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,…我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要是还活着的话 会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.97,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,995)}παγώνι
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,帕格尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.61,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(846,995)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.61,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1044,995)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,法莱那的恶灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,到底还是迷信 真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,比沙海里的微尘还要低劣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不如就此消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,早就知道了！这种事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被关在狭小的岛上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对世界一无所知！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都影响不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那种泥巴船早就不想待了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以！别来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你这秃子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这群家伙不过是螳臂当车！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,「体内鼹鼠」！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都给我上！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我跟欧尼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就总是最强的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再可别看扁咱们了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,捉只老鼠还这么磨磨唧唧的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给我马上干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我…们…总在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我来带你到外面的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.24,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1046,995)}thymia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,居然能用情念力！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,995)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1084,995)}αὔρα
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,「魂形之间」里 念纹怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼！ 尼比！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗 危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:44.85,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(928,995)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,恶灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这种事 怎么可能发生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对了！ 就是因为触犯了禁忌！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.61,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,995)}όρκα
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪奥尔卡的昏招！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.94,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,995)}δαίμονας
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,让恶灵觉醒了…！ 都怪他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 蓬蓬头！ 这是怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,查奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯！ 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼！ 欧尼！ 你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,本来是我一直想要你不要丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到 居然倒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思… 这是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让你搭上这条船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,布奇…艾吉洛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,多不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次见欧尼你哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼你或许觉得 要是不能从泥鲸出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就没有意义了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我…其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,比你的以为的还要…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可以说是满足于现状吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一面憧憬着外面的世界 一面在那座岛上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,每天跟你一起眺望不变的蓝天与大海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就最好不过了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没有意义的…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是跟你们相见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,连我活在这里的理由都不存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我会一直等着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,让我见识见识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拂却沙尘 这个世界的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,尼比！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,…哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.94,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1022,995)}ολιβίνης
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是奥莉薇尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,奥莉…薇尼斯…
